{Name}{}{Seymour}
{DescAliveShort}{}{You see a spore plant.}
{DescAliveFull}{}{You see Seymour the spore plant.}
{DescAliveFull}{}{You see a spore plant that somehow radiates an aura of intelligence.}
{Speech 1}{}{Initial preferences}
{Speech 1 Answer 3}{}{Dumb}
