{Speech 2}{}{Psst! Hey! Hey, pal! Over here!@@C'mere! I promise I won't hurt you.@@Come on. You scared of a plant?@@Over here! Let's get to it!@@Yes, I'm a talking plant. Get over it and talk to me.}
{Speech 3}{}{Hi! Nice weather we've been having, huh?}
{Speech 3 Answer 5}{}{Yoo talk?}
{Speech 3 Answer Exit}{}{Rrr?}
{Speech 4}{}{Hi! Nice weather we've been having, huh?}
{Speech 4 Answer 6}{}{Excuse me, but is this the plant that's talking?}
{Speech 4 Answer 7}{}{Are you connected with that scientist in any way?}
{Speech 4 Answer Exit}{}{Bye.}
{Speech 5}{}{Yes, I do talk. Better than some people, it seems. I'd smile at you right now, but I just don't have a mouth. [It laughs] Say, could you do me a big favor?}
{Speech 5 Answer Exit}{}{'Es.}
{Speech 5 Answer Exit*}{}{Nuh.}
{Speech 6}{}{Yes, I do talk. Better than some people, it seems. I'd smile at you right now, but I just don't have a mouth. [It laughs] Say, could you do me a big favor?}
{Speech 6 Answer Exit}{}{Bye.}
{Speech 7}{}{Oh, yes, the Professor. He grew me from a tiny spore and nurtured me... but I realized from an early age that if I were to act as smart as I truly am, he'd cut me into pieces to examine me.  So, I played dumb and got planted out here. It's nice... but I'd like to branch out a little. Y'know, maybe get planted someplace else...}
{Speech 7 Answer Exit}{}{Uh... huh. I gotta go. Bye.}
